GJLAJLOPLJG: The Sublime Anemograna seem to be able to guide powerful winds, forming them into whirling currents capable of sucking opponents in. Use this unique feature to gather great numbers of opponents such that you can deal them all a decisive blow!
ACMKINKCHFC:
You will obtain the following buffs according to the number of Sublime Anemograna you obtain:
1: When you switch characters, you will generate a cyclone that will pull nearby opponents in for 3s. This effect can trigger once every 5s.
2: Enhances the effect of the cyclone such that it will deal 1 instance of Anemo DMG to nearby opponents every 0.7s.
3: Enhances the effect of the cyclone by increasing the Anemo DMG it deals. The cyclone now persists for 5s.

GJLAJLOPLJG: No matter how strong the foe, no one will find an attack from above easy to deal with. Use the enhanced jumping power imparted by the Sublime Anemograna and the vertical spaces of the battlefield to surprise your opponents!
ACMKINKCHFC:
You will obtain the following buffs according to the number of Sublime Anemograna you obtain:
1: Characters' jumping power is greatly increased and Plunging Attacks deal 40% increased DMG.
2: Characters' jumping power is greatly increased and Plunging Attacks deal 80% increased DMG.
3: Characters' jumping power is greatly increased, Stamina Consumption is decreased by 30%, and Plunging Attacks deal 150% increased DMG.
